---
title: Italian Lamb & Veggie Ragu with Fettuccine, Feta & Basil
description: This sumptuous yet simple pasta is absolute decadence, from the rich lamb ragu infused with Italian herbs to the topping of sweet roasted capsicum and crumbly feta. Don’t be too surprised if the bowls are licked clean!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/italian-lamb-basil-ragu-6a4bc538.jpg
